I've made this numerous times for my family since my daugher was forced to eliminate wheat from her diet. I use Muir Glen organic chopped tomatoes instead of fresh in the cold months in New England. It's fabulous with some grated aged gouda sprinkled on top. Super fast, easy and always satisfying.

Rating: 4
Made with anchovy paste as suggested. Used 1/2 local yellow cherry tomatoes and 1/2 local mini-plum tomatoes. It worked very well.

Rating: 3
This is wonderful with brown rice. I added a bit of anchovy paste and it improved the flavor. This would be best if made during the summer when tomatoes are at their peak. I used winter tomatoes and the flavor lacked somewhat. Would definitely make this again.

Rating: 3
